column5: ...I just agreed to buy a new to me boat and today in the mail is a radioworld catalogue.
There's never been a better time to lock in 5 year mortgage..
Sounds like more of a solution than a problem
I just did that as well. And we're bridging so I have 2 mortgages right now.
Just picked up my Terrova + I-Pilot Link from Radioworld today   Very easy to spend $$$ in that place, lol.
Last time I was there to get a gps/finder I picked-up two inflatable lifevests that were right by the check-out. Impulse buy.
I just dropped $13K on a new outboard and mercmonitor gauge.
